Execution:
----------

./Camera Filename(.obj) yaw pitch roll (camera rotation [rad]) tx ty tz (camera translation [cm]) f (focal length [cm] > 0) cx (X camera principal point [pixels]) cy (Y camera principal point [pixels]) r (pixel/cm) indexes (points indexes file name)

# Frontal view (e.g)
./Camera <mesh.obj> 0 0 0 0 0 -200 0.2 640 480 100 <point_indexes>

# Right lateral view (e.g)
./Camera <mesh.obj> 0 1.5707 0 -200 0 0 0.2 640 480 100 <point_indexes>

# Left lateral view (e.g)
./Camera <mesh.obj> 0 -1.5707 0 200 0 0 0.2 640 480 100 <point_indexes>
